snippet.title: Amber Heard Lies to Court About Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #Lies

In this episode of Jolly's Rants, Jolly continues his up to date information on the depp vs the sun trial.  Today Amber Heard gave her first testimony where she blatantly lied about events that took place in question
